{"tid":186891,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"破滅魔劍究竟有幾犀利?","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T09:24:46.000Z","uid":92780,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"330dc951538338cda10c9425e5567b1dae2eee8f","tid":186891,"uid":92780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"破滅魔劍究竟有幾犀利?<br />\n<br />\n由太空射落去火星表面需要 ~ 4s 嘅時間. 假設部MS嘅高度喺太空站同哈勃望遠鏡之間, take mean: <br />\n(360 + 560)/2 = 460 km<br />\n<br />\n跌落去平均速度為:<br />\n460/4 = 115 km/s<br />\n<br />\n唔計大氣層, 我哋而家計算魔劍最初嘅速度, MARS G acceleration: 3.77 m/s^2<br />\n<br />\ns = ut + 1&frasl;2at^2<br />\n460000 = 4u + 0.5 x 3.77 x 4^2<br />\nu = 114992.46 m/s<br />\n<br />\n揸住把魔嘅劍MS 係EB-06 グレイズ , 高度為17.8 m我哋而家用比例計碌劍嘅長度&amp;大小:<br />\n<br />\n高度 :  EB06 ~ 250 pixel高   魔劍 ~  295 pixel長<br />\n(295pixel/250pixel) x 17.8 = 21m<br />\n闊度 :  ~10 pixel = ~ 0.7m<br />\nr^2 x pi x height = 碌劍體積<br />\n0.35^2 x pi x 21 = 8.08 m^3<br />\n<br />\n假設材料為Ta - 10% W, 一種超硬同高熱抵抗嘅材料, NASA都有用.  Density 為 16.8 (g/cm^3) :<br />\n<br />\n魔劍 = 135744 kg<br />\n<br />\n我哋而家可以計算佢嘅動能:<br />\nKE = 1&frasl;2 mv^2<br />\ninitial KE = 8.97 x 10^14 J<br />\n<br />\n8.97 x 10^14 J 等於214388噸 tnt<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大約等於廣島核彈16.5 倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0a6hMbV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0a6hMbV.gif&h=df444915&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03de266c3afd380ea59443f7ab05a4c1f0d43962","tid":186891,"uid":52263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b725745c0408e27cbe09bb57d8e7999c44c027","tid":186891,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"破滅魔劍殺唔殺得死噴火龍X？"},{"pid":"1a1d66a7d3bf4f6eb7b816fdc83229051198366b","tid":186891,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>破滅魔劍殺唔殺得死噴火龍X？</blockquote><br />\n已經得，噴火龍X係就黎無血時先鎖血...<br />\n但破滅魔劍射佢一下已經可以秒殺，噴火龍X用唔切鎖血技..<br />\n係破滅魔劍既勝利"},{"pid":"8b6fd70f1e5f163d2fb70b4a01432277925f8a51","tid":186891,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:18:10.000Z","msg":"吶，你知道嗎"},{"pid":"1157c4007a9d7daa3b36dbacc48c7228ea228cfe","tid":186891,"uid":9262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>破滅魔劍殺唔殺得死噴火龍X？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076c973cfe035da37a6b940c10e2f9ae32cb15b5","tid":186891,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>破滅魔劍殺唔殺得死噴火龍X？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鎖左血　<br />\n變左箭豬都殺死噴火龍X"},{"pid":"326d8461cd3e5ea67022a0a86c00ffe5bdbdc550","tid":186891,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"極速115公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265790f831cf8c6059447d9049757aa222506326","tid":186891,"uid":39698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dec4d58b122d6047a7c53306a2a21690795a279","tid":186891,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吶，你知道嗎</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>吶，你知道嗎</blockquote><br />\n魔劍落下的速度是秒速百公里"},{"pid":"55ecd7b603adf7018c9c00c7cecc7154d92ebae8","tid":186891,"uid":34468,