"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>破滅魔劍Vs獨孤九劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點個勁d</blockquote><br />\n破滅魔劍傻仔都識用<br />\n獨孤九劍要根基好再學幾十年先識用</blockquote><br />\n一招破箭式搞掂佢</blockquote><br />\n你要首先分清楚佢係箭定劍</blockquote><br />\n用弓射出黎既劍(箭?)"},{"pid":"94a529639de195a899d571019ac4ffecd541472b","tid":186891,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>破滅魔劍Vs獨孤九劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點個勁d</blockquote><br />\n破滅魔劍傻仔都識用<br />\n獨孤九劍要根基好再學幾十年先識用</blockquote><br />\n一招破箭式搞掂佢</blockquote><br />\n你要首先分清楚佢係箭定劍</blockquote><br />\n用弓射出黎既劍(箭?)</blockquote><br />\n乾昆大羅移"},{"pid":"713ebc0f76c623c2d0ddce44b7776df5be467a19","tid":186891,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>破滅魔劍Vs獨孤九劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點個勁d</blockquote><br />\n破滅魔劍傻仔都識用<br />\n獨孤九劍要根基好再學幾十年先識用</blockquote><br />\n一招破箭式搞掂佢</blockquote><br />\n你要首先分清楚佢係箭定劍</blockquote><br />\n用弓射出黎既劍(箭?)</blockquote><br />\n乾昆大羅移</blockquote><br />\n你隻手掂到佢都已經穿撚左啦，仲點移<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a44e460eb3f06bacdef3dddac5c76d2dde39bc","tid":186891,"uid":57122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知點work<br />\n唔係制導武器<br />\nms內置既火控真係夠計算力同觀測能力測到風速而且修正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支野既速度快到避唔到既話根本正支野燒完都到唔到地面 仲有個動能做出黎既衝擊波都爆得死友軍 完全唔知點做到<br />\n至於加工精度問題 簡單d講你切歪1mm 重心歪1mm 成支野就會報廢<br />\n點睇製造魔劍既成套工業同材料同電子技術都似領先架垃圾高達幾個世代<br />\n<br />\n咁多黑科技 唔打外星人真係哂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"